<title>Amah Ka Zuon</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu hehpihna ka het phetin,
 Kipak in amah zuon ka;
 A hehpihna thuhaw ka hetin,
 Kipak in chawian zel ka.

[V2]
 Amah ka zuon, kipahna ka mui,
 Ka thagau le A hukdam;
 Vana ka mun ding a siem achun,
 Kum khawsawt in chawling ka.

[V3]
 2. Ka lungkhamna cheng cheng A chiehpih,
 Kipakin kei um tang ka;
 A kawma kumsawt kipahna chu,
 Kipak takin chang tangka.

[V4]
 3. Chawmlo kalin hungkit paiin tin,
 A hehpihte pui dingin;
 A van In nuom achun pui ina,
 Nawp tawp lo gam nuom achun.

[V5]
 4. Ni cheng gitlohna'n ei tuom mahleh,
 Hang takin ding ing ka ting;
 A lopinan ei panpih in tin,
 Thepna haw zo ngei ingka.</lyrics>
</song>